{"tid":1931120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【831CCTV】3月18星期三有結果，有沒人推post關注？","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T09:48:36.000Z","uid":156828,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"95e5ced9a66da6865b8ec4afa9eb33bbe7937510","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n【831CCTV】3月18星期三有結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1925525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1925525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHi，我係之前向法庭申請831同9月1太子站與荔枝角站嘅閉路電視記錄嗰個人。單案會喺3月18（星期三）晏晝2點半喺高院判。雖然個官係周家明，而法治已死已經係common sense。但我都希望今次可以好似上次出禁制令咁，呀周官可以有個好嘅判決。<br />\n<br />\n831半年，我唔知仲有幾多人仲記得同仲堅持緊。我有嘅只有丁點希望。<br />\n贏輸都好，感謝一班律師團隊，同所有幫過手嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"87af2713e7624a002bbfded3ecb0db3f0ea84bef","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"先推5次為敬<br />\n1/5"},{"pid":"543fdd3feb294b829b0b07c124ff513bd1406746","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"94a55db3a31b4eaf506b23da1fa2b7b45bff97ed","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"fb6289773b5c595f276753dde504d04806f8de24","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"cbaaf43f567f470b59a3ee73578f42c4918da12f","tid":1931120,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b29010eebb97cab31f5ba9db1a7def6fca40c8b","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"5/5"},{"pid":"79fb97761d31c48ea2e98753dcd36003604d0991","tid":1931120,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:02:51.000Z"